R

RemoveSpurs - Class in plugins
This image processing tool removes small irregularities (i.e., spurs) on the boundaries of objects in a Boolean raster image.
RemoveSpurs() - Constructor for class plugins.RemoveSpurs
 
Resample - Class in plugins
This tool will resample the values from one or more source image files into a destination image file using one of three resampling methods including, nearest neighbour, bilinear interpolation, and cubic convolution.
Resample() - Constructor for class plugins.Resample
 
RGBtoIHS(double, double, double) - Method in class plugins.PanSharpening
Converts RGB colour values to IHS colour values
RGBtoIHS - Class in plugins
This tool transforms three raster images of multispectral data (red, green, and blue channels) into their equivalent intensity, hue, and saturation (IHS; sometimes HSI or HIS) images.
RGBtoIHS() - Constructor for class plugins.RGBtoIHS
